tweets.text:
@whitehouse I commend @realDonaldTrump
for embracing remigration — that’s the right vision. But to actually finish the job, we need full mass deportation, not just targeted enforcement.   

Without the big hammer, it’s like having yin without yang — the system won’t reset. The president gets it at a deep level, and pairing these two is the complete formula.  Mass deportations are the solution!

